        <updateDate>2020-03-05T21:59:03Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>This bill requires the National Highway Traffic Safety Administration to conduct a study on the (1) behavior of individuals using electric scooters while under the influence of alcohol or drugs; (2) involvement of electric scooters in traffic accidents; and (3) effects on pedestrian, scooter user, and motorist safety resulting from the lack of laws governing the use of electric scooters and a lack of training on their safe operation.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>To require the Secretary of Transportation to conduct a study on the unsafe use of electric scooters, and for other purposes.</title>
